text: Chacha Eke Faani (born 17 July 1987) is a Nigerian actress. ==Biography== Chacha Eke was born in Ebonyi State where she had her Bachelor of Science degree in accountancy from Ebonyi State University. In 2013, She got married to Austin Ikechukwu Faani. ==Selected filmography== * Village Love * The End is Near * Money and Blood * Black Val * Chisom: The Wife Material * A Dance for the Prince * Pure Heart ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Nigerian actors Category:Living people Category:1987 births
title: Chacha Eke
